Base.ErrorVariableContents: Error bij genereren tabellen vanuit beaufort

Base.Explanation: Copy a variable to the session variable list. Both the name and value of the variable are copied. If the variable already exists in the session variable list, the value is overwritten.

ArrayElement.Name: Variable name
ArrayElement.Description: The name of the variable to be copied from the project variable list to the session variable list (example: %ConnectionString%).

Base.ErrorVariableContents: Fout bij laden van AD Gebruikers voor Beuafort Koppeling
Error bij matchen van beaufort gebruikers aan ad

Base.Explanation: Delete multiple variables from the variable list. If one or more variables do not exist, no error is generated.

ArrayElement.Name: Variable names
ArrayElement.Description: The names of one or more variables that must be deleted from the variable list (example: %FirstName%, %MiddleName%, %LastName%).
